Canadians to Have ‘Inflationary’ Feeling, CI Investment’s Bushell Says

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-05-10T17:13:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/canadians-to-have-inflationary-feeling-ci-investment-s-bushell-says.html
Canadians will have inflationary
“feeling” in 2011, said Eric Bushell, chief investment
officer, Signature Global Advisors, CI Investments. Bushell
spoke at the Bloomberg Canada Economic Summit in Toronto today.  “We’ve taken a bit of a defensive stance,” Bushell said.  For more on the Bloomberg Canada Economic Summit,  To contact the reporter on this story:
